  "content": "<p data-pid=\"bpGiOBzV\">写双链笔记的人，也会做大纲节点，把一个主题下的笔记整理出来。</p><h2>比如 Andy 的笔记（汉化两百余篇）</h2><h3><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/599606352\" class=\"internal\">§ 严肃研究知识工作（Stripe 融合讨论，2019-12-12）</a></h3><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8e82aa4c58b4dea45b8f8919d5740ba_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1330\" data-rawheight=\"1386\" data-original-token=\"v2-f8e82aa4c58b4dea45b8f8919d5740ba\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cdeb2deae80de30e34793e569e042777_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1330\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f8e82aa4c58b4dea45b8f8919d5740ba_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1330&#39; height=&#39;1386&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1330\" data-rawheight=\"1386\" data-original-token=\"v2-f8e82aa4c58b4dea45b8f8919d5740ba\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cdeb2deae80de30e34793e569e042777_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1330\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f8e82aa4c58b4dea45b8f8919d5740ba_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f8e82aa4c58b4dea45b8f8919d5740ba_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><h3><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/533129885\" class=\"internal\">§笔记写作系统</a></h3><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-664dbb06d244ab344fc51cb081bba1ca_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1160\" data-rawheight=\"1394\" data-original-token=\"v2-664dbb06d244ab344fc51cb081bba1ca\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-57d4c0b0f783fdfcde16a25b9b254012_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox